d06aef82d55246b6063165f567514274fd","tid":995604,"uid":220220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b67c8a7fc4d5dd8d7e6264b888e4438ed71a152a","tid":995604,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"好處：<br />\n解鎖部機或、平時上網/用app入密碼或者畀錢個陣乜撚都唔使郁，自動搞店，比起touch id要成日郁隻拇指真係爽好多（呢樣用過先會，就咁講好難體會到）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n岩岩訓醒因為隻眼擘唔大所以成q日解唔到鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到好凍／空氣好撚差既地方、病撚左或者而家流感好勁要口罩既話就肯unlock唔到，成個傻鳩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"個mon咁光夜麻麻 或者朝早起身 拎出嚟殘親隻眼<br />\n人多或者係街用好撚老監<br />\n隻手污糟 直情唔想拎出嚟<br />\n解鎖速度始終是唔夠指紋解鎖快<br />\n我依家用iPhone X 打橫 打斜 掉轉部電話就解唔到鎖<br />\n好撚後悔買咗ipx 🙄"},{"pid":"9893fcdc585c2b8f59b428879fa9e0fc56a51f19","tid":995604,"uid":78666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"戴口罩用唔到已經扣80分啦"},{"pid":"601cc83ad6bcb59613b11271830c3e523f8977e7","tid":995604,"uid":351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"上堂/開會睇電話要望住部機先unlock到"},{"pid":"15ebb5098b91c8ec7b118c8feec575f64cf76898","tid":995604,"uid":11964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"465bda4c02ceccafd6958da8653e96f267d5158e","tid":995604,"uid":20729,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"用左一排xs 暫時黎講 Face id 係好暗環境準度同速度都差咁啲<br />\n但一拎起部就locked 睇message 幾正<br />\nTouch id 有手汗就好易fail <br />\n要試幾次先unlock到<br />\n但用Apple pay同App Store就方便過Face id<br />\n要撳兩下power掣<br />\n兩樣有好有唔好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"強烈建議face &amp; touch共存<br />\n做咩要分黨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5e9caee107bc68a54b19a817d40ffbbc177dc9","tid":995604,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"其實有FACE ID人地睇唔到訊息<br />\n用TOUCH ID個D我成日走去偷睇人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aee53ec8fc7b996294368901753bf01dec7c71b","tid":995604,"uid":52524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"其實呢兩樣野suppose應該係要共存<br />\n邊有理由要2選1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429181e3b1ab35926d6e04d9cb4cbe8ba6a798a9","tid":995604,"uid":42884,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"同時有部iPhone 7公司機同XS自家機。<br />\n用慣FaceID已經番唔到轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n1. 我住喺紐約，呢排日日帶手套，iPhone 7永遠都唔能打密碼，XS就直接解到鎖<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以等人地睇唔到我啲message<br />\n<br />\n3. Apple Pay 係用faceID 方便啲。如果你係慣左放部機去terminal 到先touchID,如果你手汗多左/感覺唔到手指，會好7。FaceID 就咁㩒兩下就得先放落去，對我嚟講係方便左<br />\n<br />\n4. FaceID唔好嘅就係瞓醒嗰一下唔太work"},{"pid":"7567753fc5105efd8ca860010027b436776d217c","tid":995604,"uid":158145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為係一年前既沉底post"},{"pid":"5bfce3b4b4c4a05ef098558bfe53f41b12014252","tid":995604,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e1c7de6b93a414be7178a5c27e2905a8306e399","tid":995604,"uid":5846,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"1ed49eb7311edea59bea096c353b9e120b79496c","tid":995604,"uid":168366,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"82658777adc8f8aab668a5ee3b62f5c178c1a95a","tid":995604,"uid":5846,"like":11,"dislike":11,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"又黎褲袋開鎖論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:52:54.000Z","msg":"的確係好撚快喎個種爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你講緊利與弊嘛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"褲袋開到